meta_description: The purpose of this community is to appreciate and spread awareness about the essential role that drone pilots serve for the rest of society. For far too long we’ve suffered under the burden of dronephobia, and we’ve decided that it’s time for this to come to an end. This is a guild for drone pilots to have fun, share memes and stories, and give each other helpful advice. Official partners of +neoliberal.
